{"tid":1577233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【表揚香港警察！！！】眾籌寄信畀黑警鄰居","createTime":"2019-09-17T15:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T09:59:27.000Z","uid":258069,"like":114,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"1e1030505d3b2b6142840dbbd4ad1cf5e372a8e7","tid":1577233,"uid":258069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T15:02:44.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲大家好：<br />\n<br />\n黑警由612 到而家做咗咁多好事<br />\n由<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">打手足</span></span>、<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">姦手足</span></span>到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">殺手足</span></span> 到做齊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，到而家一個<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">麻包袋</span></strong></span>都重未淘到返嚟<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，我代大家行多步 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我會將黑警資料寄畀佢所居住嘅整個屋苑</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等佢成個屋苑都知道佢係擔任緊 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港警察</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n學藍屍廢老話齋  <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">行得正 企得正 怕乜嘢畀人知佢係 做黑警</span></span><br />\n<br />\n等佢哋可以得到成個屋苑嘅照顧同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">保護</span></span> 仲有 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">愛戴</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前佢哋出動防暴接狗仔狗女返學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次就<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">逼到班狗要出動老解接放工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UyHkxBW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUyHkxBW.png&h=b969ab1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過咁 小弟只係一個日日<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">三餐食方包同indomie嘅貧困小朋友</span></span><br />\n<br />\n用黑白印完<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">寄350户已經要成千銀</span></strong></span><br />\n所以希望可以眾籌完成呢件事<br />\n有關財務同支出絕對會公開透明<br />\n<br />\n眾籌條Link 喺度：<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/【表揚香港警察！！！】眾籌寄信畀黑警鄰居/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%E3%80%90%E8%A1%A8%E6%8F%9A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%EF%BC%81%EF%BC%81%EF%BC%81%E3%80%91%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E5%AF%84%E4%BF%A1%E7%95%80%E9%BB%91%E8%AD%A6%E9%84%B0%E5%B1%85%2F&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5NmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=496b42cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/【表揚香港警察！！！】眾籌寄信畀黑警鄰居/</a>"},{"pid":"197195697156019624c1aa047b9309265b9f1784","tid":1577233,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T15:06:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"0f266aa002fd95947a44d79f13b038bda962e3a8","tid":1577233,"uid":258069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e1030505d3b2b61